<br />\n而唔係排緊隊既佢地<br />\n<br />\n個港女覺得阿姐呻果句係侮辱緊佢地<br />\n本身呢一點就係港女自己對號入座<br />\n<br />\n其二 佢話個阿姐撞左佢朋友個袋一下<br />\n個阿姐係咪特登撞佢友人個袋呢<br />\n同埋佢友人個袋係咪真係阻住條路呢<br />\n<br />\n港女自己講返呢單野<br />\n我反而覺得佢係有心啄住個阿姐 想做鳩佢"},{"pid":"77f26daf48cd22641f42dea94cda1b33d65ed9f7","tid":796100,"uid":119330,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"47e104fdeb304a444fad28e228fcbc1108bdfb2b","tid":796100,"uid":153239,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"a4aed7669d543e105e3e8da25ebc11e3e1ee27dd","tid":796100,"uid":119330,"like":4,"dislike":16,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"a98c31b3599a72fd95370e88b7aa8643822c24f2","tid":796100,"uid":58247,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T13:48:26.000Z","msg":"佢唔係即場同阿姐講話投訴佢咩(佢個版本)"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T13:51:20.000Z","msg":"聽住先啦<br />\n個事實就係個阿姐真係比佢搞到無左份工<br />\n<br />\nbtw 個廁所咁多人<br />\n又唔見其他人同個阿姐有衝突<br />\n總之事實各有各講<br />\n但係咪全部呢 無人知"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T13:55:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你既諗法根本已經有前設<br />\n唔好係有意無意之間透路有中立既成份<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T14:05:38.000Z","msg":"中立個意思<br />\n係指件事係咪真係港女所講<br />\n佢係受害者呢<br />\n<br />\n好多時去投訴既人<br />\n本身就係對件事帶左副有色眼鏡去睇<br />\n然後就將件事無限放大"},{"pid":"fd1e8f6ee4d7df83746aaeae398bb6ea56be0fb0","tid":796100,"uid":46896,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T14:06:47.000Z","msg":"呢次都係信女fans多啲，知唔知十個清潔阿姐九個啲態度都好西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"184efd30887e3d99dd8a4dc192c563f80797e29c","tid":796100,"uid":164368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T14:06:53.000Z","msg":"有冇絲係紅館做？"},{"pid":"f2a01f0135136a5becbb160a02debd7de95281a4","tid":796100,"uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-